high_descs: Turn around, go halfway across the room, turn left, head to the wall and turn left towards the white table.
Pick up the spatula to the left of the knife on the table.
Turn right, go halfway across the room, turn left, head to the fridge, turn right and go to the sink.
Put the spatula in the left side of the sink, rinse it off and pick it back up.
Turn around and go to the table.
Put the spatula on the table in front of the tomato.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean spatula on the table.

high_descs: Turn around and go forward, then turn left to go to the wall, then turn right to face the white table.
Pick up the leftmost spatula from the white table.
Turn right and go forward, then turn left and go toward the fridge, then turn right to go to the left sink basin.
Wash the spatula in the sink.
Turn right and move forward, then turn right and go straight ahead to the white table.
Put the spatula on the white table.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean spatula on the white table.

high_descs: Turn around and take a step then turn left and walk to the wall then turn right.
Pick up the spatula that's in front of you near the wall on the left.
Turn right and walk to the sink that's to your left across the room and stand in front of it facing it so you can use it.
Wash the spatula in the sink and then pick it back up and shut off the water.
Turn right and take a step then turn right and walk to the table.
Put the spatula on the big tomato on the table in front of you to the left of the salt shaker.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean spatula on the table.
